dcterms:description: The OhioT1DM dataset contains data from 12 patients suffering from type-I diabetes measured via fitness bands over 8 weeks. It includes high-frequency variables such as continuous glucose monitoring (CGM) blood glucose levels recorded every 5 minutes, as well as lower frequency variables like carbohydrate estimates and exercise intensity.
dcterms:title: OhioT1DM dataset
